snippet.title: FloCity_Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Canal digging - a unique gameplay of city builder is offered in FloCity. Dig freeform canal networks for run-time AI shipping, reform shorelines, smooth traffic flow, develop lands around the busy ports... before the resource island sinks!

Now available on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2345960/FloCity/
